  <summary date="2017-03-13T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Social Security Must Avert Identity Loss (MAIL) Act of 2017

This bill amends title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) of the Social Security Act to direct the Social Security Administration to ensure that no document it sends by mail includes a complete Social Security account number unless necessary.</summary>
